<h1>NIF is at  <a href="http://www.neuinfo.org">http://www.neuinfo.org</a> </h1>
<h2>What is NIF?</h2>
<p>Funded by the NIH Blueprint for Neuroscience Research, NIF is a  government-led contract project providing a dynamic inventory of Web-based neuroscience resources: data, materials, and tools accessible via any computer connected to the Internet. NIF advances neuroscience research by enabling discovery and access to public research data and tools worldwide through an open source, networked environment.  NIF uses the following multiple tools and approaches to enable searches concurrently across multiple resource types:</p>
<ul>
 <li><a href="http://www.neuinfo.org/nif_tools/data_federation.shtm">NIF Data
     Federation</a></li>

 <li><a href="http://www.neuinfo.org/nif_tools/literature_corpus.shtm">NIF
     Literature</a></li>

 <li><a href="http://www.neuinfo.org/vocabularies/index.shtm">NIF Vocabularies</a></li>

 <li><a href="http://disco.neuinfo.org/webportal">NIF DISCO</a></li>

 <li><a href="http://disco.neuinfo.org/linkout/linkout.do">NIF LinkOut Broker</a>
     (Beta)</li>

 <li><a href="http://www.neuinfo.org/nif_tools/mynif.shtm">MyNIF</a> (Beta)</li>

 <li><a href="http://www.neuinfo.org/registering_resources.shtm">Resource
     Registration Tools</a></li>

 <li><a href="http://www.neuinfo.org/nif/nifgwt.html?query=DrugDependentGeneDB">Genetics
     of Drug Addiction Database</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Is your resource registered with NIF?  <a href="http://neuinfo.org/cindylite/nominate.html">Click here to recommend it and other resources</a> to NIF; then get the <a href="http://www.neuinfo.org/registered_resources.shtm">"Registered with NIF"</a> logo and place it on your website to let the research community know you are  part of the Neuroscience Information Framework!</p>

<a href="http://www.neuinfo.org"><img src="images/registered_with_nif_button.jpg" alt="registered_with_nif_button" width="125" height="40" border="0"/></a>

<h2>Search NIF now at <a href="http://www.neuinfo.org">http://www.neuinfo.org</a>!  </h2>

	     		 
		 
